headline: TSCO Increases Dividend by 4.3% to $0.96 per Share for 2026
summary: We recently published an article titled 12 Best Retail Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On February 11, Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ:TSCO) announced that its Board of Directors increased the annualized dividend by $0.04, or 4.3% year over year, to $0.96 per share for 2026, marking the company’s 17th consecutive year of dividend growth.
